# Package manager: pnpm only

This repo uses **pnpm** (`pnpm-lock.yaml`). Never use `npm install` or `yarn` for dependencies.

```bash
pnpm add <pkg>
pnpm add -D <pkg>
pnpm install
pnpm exec tsc --noEmit
```

`npm install` is slower here and can fight the existing pnpm store / lockfile.
